<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap');
  
  .font-sans { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; }
  
  .cleaning-hero-bg {
    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581578731117-104f2a412727?q=80&w=1920&auto=format&fit=crop');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }
</style>

<div class="font-sans text-gray-800 bg-white">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center cleaning-hero-bg text-white overflow-hidden pt-12">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/60 to-black/30 z-0"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-blue-600/90 backdrop-blur rounded-full text-white text-xs font-bold mb-6">
        ✨ 수도권 전 지역 무료 출장 견적
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
        공간의 가치를 높이는<br>
        <span class="text-blue-400">프리미엄 클리닝</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-200 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
        보이지 않는 미세먼지부터 유해 세균까지, <br>
        <span class="font-bold text-white">클린 싹싹</span>이 완벽하게 케어해드립니다.
      </p>
      
